Articles.Content:
Orionkermin -

The DRE config needs to be updated to this:

    @PART[Corvus_Heatshield]:FOR[DeadlyReentry]{	!MODULE[ModuleAblator]{}	!RESOURCE[Ablator]{}        @thermalMassModifier = 1	@maxTemp = 1800	MODULE	{		name = ModuleHeatShield		ablativeResource = AblativeShielding		lossExp = -6000		lossConst = 20		pyrolysisLossFactor = 10000		reentryConductivity = 0.025		ablationTempThresh = 500		skinHeatConductivity = 0.25	}	RESOURCE	{		name = AblativeShielding		amount = 100		maxAmount = 100	}}

The current CFG prevents the heatshield from ablating properly ![:)](//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif)
